Audrey Christie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Audrey_Christie 0 Audrey Christie (June 27, 1912 – December 19, 1989) was an American actress. She appeared in the films Keeper of the Flame, Deadline – U.S.A., Carousel, Splendor in the Grass, The Unsinkable Molly Brown, Harlow, Frankie and Johnny, The Ballad of Josie, Mame and Harper Valley PTA. She died of emphysema on December 19, 1989, at her home in West Hollywood, California at age 77. Audrey_Christie ( June_27_,_1912 – December_19_,_1989 ) was an_American_actress .
